    <description>Package Description</description>
    <releaseNotes>'Merged PR 11180: Merged PR 11081: [PrimeFastRasterTestMethod] Enabled MaxDefectCount.'
'Merged PR 10862: [GetRepairDff][SetRepairDff] Adding optional parameters to configuration file for retrieving and registering Dff tokens'
'Merged PR 10727: [Array Repair] Adding controller when identifying a unique set of values for the logical address'
'Merged PR 10665: [Array][R2F] Fixing conditional for insufficient space for static data and adding error case'
'Merged PR 9985: [TOS4] [Array] [PvalMigration] Migrating test plans from TOS3 to TOS4'
'Merged PR 10314: [RepairToFuse] Adding exit port 2 used when there is insufficient space to insert fuse data'
'Merged PR 10343: Fixing Incorrect CMPR_LA Ituff Data Logging for MBIST repair extension'</releaseNotes>
    <copyright>Copyright (2005) (2025) Intel Corporation</copyright>
